title: Client not starting
body: When I try to start my League of Legends client, it gives me an error about it not running the configuration side-by-side or something? I don't really have any idea what is going on.

replies.body: Hmmmmm that doesn't sound like an error I'm familiar with. Could you possibly grab a screenshot of what it says or explain it a bit more so I can find the best way to fix this for ya?
Sorry Broporo. It was an issue with my laptop not the client I apologize.

No worries bud! Was willing to do my best regardless of what the error was for xD!
